      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; solver residual convergence criteria documented.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, explicit quantification of numerical solver error beyond residual convergence is not required. Residuals converged to 1×10⁻⁶ for all equations. Factor scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 table."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
