      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; turbulence model selection justified by literature precedent for centrifugal pump hemolysis.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published consensus for centrifugal blood pump CFD (Hariharan et al. 2011, Herbertson et al. 2013). Model-form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
