      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; input parameter sensitivity to blood viscosity documented qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "Sensitivity of hemolysis index to ±10% variation in blood viscosity assessed qualitatively; results change by less than 4%. Formal input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
