      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; experimental sample size and lot-to-lot variability noted.",
      "rationale": "FDA GCBP experimental dataset comprises triplicate runs per operating point with a single bovine blood lot. Sample variability is reported as CV < 8%. Statistical characterization of inter-lot variability not required at MRL 2."
